h and verifies the public JUL level parsing behavior, but the two legacy `KnownLevelBuilder.add(...)` call sites remain unreachable on the current supported JDK without violating the constraints.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_061ae871c3261499016a23839ca8ac8194863679ddf023648b\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"oca/gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 40656, \"output\": 858, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 41514, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1780712334798, \"responseId\": \"resp_061ae871c3261499016a23838fb2e48194ba68ae8bb9c6f00b\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n[recv] agent_end\n[send] get_state\n[recv] get_state success\n  sessionFile: ../../../../../../../../.pi/agent/sessions/--home-vjovanov-c-forge-forge1-graalvm-reachability-metadata-forge-local_repositories-forge_worktrees-7920-b5605542--/2026-06-06T02-13-25-681Z_019e9ab4-e031-756c-af85-6c4025c307bc.jsonl\n  sessionId: 019e9ab4-e031-756c-af85-6c4025c307bc\n[send] get_session_stats\n[recv] get_session_stats success\n  tokens: input=149191 output=10833 cacheRead=678400 cacheWrite=0 total=838424\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
